    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A silvery-white metallic element of the lanthanide series, atomic no. 60, which was discovered as a component (with praseodymium) of the supposed element didymium and is used in mischmetal and some other alloys.</Note_Text>
